and relax in a natural environment?

43
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,800
It will help relieve your emotions

44
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,120
and contribute to the
next stage of treatment.

45
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,320
