Yanxu is also here.

67
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,360
He will protect me.

68
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,440
What can he do to protect you?

69
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,640
He is in a worse condition than you,

70
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,760
and besides, he is a patient himself.

71
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,720
You, as a young girl,

72
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,520
shouldn't be hanging out

73
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,920
with a boy.

74
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,000
It's absolutely not acceptable.

75
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:03,160
Mom.

76
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,000
Tongtong,

77
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:07,720
