78
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:10,040
I'll take care of your dad.

79
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,640
Thank you, Mom.

80
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,000
I knew you're the best.

81
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,920
What's wrong with you?

82
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,840
Didn't we agree to stand together?

83
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,800
Thank you, Dad.

84
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,520
Director Xu, what do you want
to see me about?

85
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,760
No, there's nothing.

86
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,080
I was busy during the past period,

87
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,440
didn't have time to come and see you.

88
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,680
But as soon as I finished,
I came over right away.

89
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:42,960
You're being too polite,
Director Xu.

90
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,280
It's what I should do.

91
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,200
By the way,

92
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,840
how is the progress of the investigation

93
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,920
that the headquarters sent you here for?

94
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,920
Is everything going smoothly?

95
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,120
Thank you for your concern, Director Xu.

96
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,000
Everything is going smoothly.

97
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,120
Dr. Li,

98
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,360
there's a problem with the data
from Zheng's office.

99
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,240
They want you to go over there.

100
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,520
Alright, I'll come right away.

101
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,520
I'll go there first.

102
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,440
When you're free,
let's have a meal together.

103
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:02,440
Sure, let's do that.

104
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,760
Tongtong.

105
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,560
What's wrong?

106
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:56,960
My parents

107
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,320
agreed so easily for us
to go out and play.

108
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,720
I have a feeling that
something isn't right.

109
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,120
Don't overthink it.

110
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,960
We finally got the chance to go out
so let's enjoy ourselves.

111
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,040
No,

112
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,200
I still can't shake off my worries.

113
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,560
Let me test it out.

114
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,120
Dad.

115
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,440
What's wrong?

116
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,960
I just woke up.

117
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:22,960
Oh,

118
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,880
did I disturb you?

119
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,160
It's nothing. What's up?

120
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,160
Nothing.

121
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:31,240
I just wanted to let you know that
we're about to leave, look!

122
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,920
Alright.

123
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,600
Got it.

124
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,960
Be safe on the road.

125
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:36,600
Okay.

126
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,000
I'll hang up now.

127
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,320
Okay.

128
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,440
Maybe I really am overthinking it.

129
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,560
Alright, let's stop thinking and
get in the car.

130
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,760
Wife, you understand
our daughter the best.

131
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,520
You knew she would
check everything in advance.

132
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,720
That's why you prepared
all these things.

133
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,360
Yes,

134
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,000
otherwise we would have been exposed.

135
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,840
Trying to challenging me?

136
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,880
You're still too young
to compete with me.

137
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,520
Catch up with them.

138
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,360
No problem.

139
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,360
Just by holding hands,

140
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,280
we almost got into an accident.

141
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,120
It was so scary.

142
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:56,120
I should have known better than
to sit in the passenger seat.

143
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,840
I told you not to come.

144
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,240
Mom, Dad, why are you here?

145
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,960
In your pajamas, too.

146
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,760
You don't need to worry about that.

147
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,800
If we hadn't come,

148
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,560
who knows what kind of trouble
you would have gotten into.

149
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,760
Tongtong, do you realize how
dangerous that was?

150
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,720
Your dad and I were following
behind you just now.

151
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,640
I was almost scared to death

152
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,400
when seeing your car suddenly
lose control.

153
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,440
It's okay.

154
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,360
This isn't okay.

155
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:25,600
Song,

156
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,200
make a call quickly.

157
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,040
Ask a mechanic to tow your car away

158
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,920
then send me the address.

159
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,440
Both of you, get in our car.

160
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,760
We'll take you there.

161
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,720
Yan Xu,

162
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,800
you sit in the passenger seat.

163
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:49,920
Okay.

164
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,720
Mansu, you're looking for me?

165
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,840
Yeah.

166
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:10,920
I asked a friend to bring you
a burn ointment.

167
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:13,720
It works quickly and won't leave scars.

168
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,720
Here you go.

169
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,160
I apologize for last time.

170
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,360
I didn't expect you to
remember the injury on my hand.

171
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,320
Thank you.

172
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,720
Mansu,

173
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,720
I advise you not to investigate
Yanxu's matter anymore.

174
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,840
Sometimes letting go is a
form of relief,

175
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,160
and it's better for both you and him.

176
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,000
Compared to the two of us,

177
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,880
I think I have a better mindset.

178
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:37,160
At least I don't have
self-harm tendencies.

179
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,800
Just leave me alone, okay?

180
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:40,920
I'll handle it myself.

181
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,360
Hello?

182
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,400
Let's meet, okay?

183
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,800
Hello, Mr. Song.

184
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,720
We have already processed your
reservation

185
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,360
for the deluxe double suite.

186
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,600
Please follow me upstairs.

187
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,840
You're quite clever

188
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,320
to choose a double room.

189
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,480
I forgot to add your room.

190
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,200
Manager,

191
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,760
could you please add another room
next to the room?

192
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:36,960
Mr. Song,

193
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,560
I apologize for the inconvenience.

194
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,960
It's currently the peak tourist season,

195
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,040
and our hotel is fully booked.

196
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,920
This kid tends to spend
money recklessly.

197
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,800
Having two rooms should be sufficient.

198
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,280
I stay with Tongtong,

199
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,160
and you can stay with your uncle.

200
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,720
Please rest assured.

201
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,160
Mr. Song has booked

202
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:57,760
our hotel's highest-standard
double suite.

203
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,760
Not to mention four people,

204
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,600
even if there are eight people,
it's not a problem.

205
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,360
I've prepared the meals and drinks.

206
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:04,160
If you have any requests,
please let me know.

207
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:06,440
No. Please show us the way.

208
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,760
This way, please.

209
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:11,160
Will Uncle be upset with me?

210
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,200
No, he won't.

211
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,760
Besides, my dad sleeps quietly,
so there's no problem. Let's go.

212
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,640
Tongtong.

213
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:35,160
Such a serious matter like insomnia,

214
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,440
you didn't even inform the family.

215
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,720
Do you know how upset I felt

216
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,720
after your dad talked to me that day?

217
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,600
Mom,

218
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,880
I keep it from you and dad

219
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,520
because I didn't want to worry you.

220
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,960
Oh, you silly child.

221
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,720
As your parents,

222
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:53,440
who else should we worry about
if not our own child?

223
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,320
Mom,

224
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:01,200
do you and dad still not believe
what I said?

225
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,120
Initially, yes,

226
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:07,120
we did find it hard to believe.

227
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,560
But upon careful consideration,

228
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:10,720
there are indeed

229
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:13,400
many unexplainable things in this world.

230
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,040
Instead of making baseless guesses,

231
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,240
we choose to believe you.

232
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:21,920
We hope that both of you
can support each other

233
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,360
and recover from it as soon as possible.

234
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,560
Mom,

235
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,160
actually, I know that

236
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,960
even though Dad may seem stern,

237
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,760
he really loves me, right?

238
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,720
Your dad

239
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,320
is tough in words but soft in actions.

240
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,160
Remember when you were born,

241
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:39,120
he would hold you in his arms,

242
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:41,320
treating you like a
delicate porcelain doll,

243
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,960
afraid of dropping or hurting you.

244
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,920
Whenever he snored in his sleep,

245
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:49,760
you would cry non-stop,

246
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,240
with your little face turning red.

247
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,240
It broke his heart.

248
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:57,440
He didn't dare to sleep
in the same room afterward

249
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,560
and would go to the sofa alone.

250
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,920
Oh, my goodness,

251
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,520
I can't believe this!

252
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:05,200
How did I not know about it?

253
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:08,920
Wait a minute,

254
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:12,000
does Dad still snore now?

255
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,720
Is his snoring bothering you?

256
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,800
Song Yanxu,

257
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,160
What's wrong?

258
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:01,400
What are you staring like that?

259
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,760
Tongtong,

260
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,440
I'm sorry.

261
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,400
Fortunately, nothing happened today.

262
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,600
Otherwise, I'd never forgive myself
for the rest of my life.

263
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:12,520
Don't take all the blame upon yourself.

264
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,640
It seems Dr. Li was right.

265
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:18,520
Our time of contact and sleep
has been getting shorter.

266
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:20,400
We need to be more careful
in the future.

267
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:24,960
I just hate that I can't
protect you well.

268
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,960
Every time, I put you in danger.

269
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,760
This time, we had Uncle and Aunt here,

270
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,160
but what about next time?

271
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:31,560
Next time...

272
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:32,960
Yanxu.

273
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:36,320
Whenever I have a problem,

274
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,800
you're always the first one to appear.

275
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:40,320
You knew I wanted to join the
symphony orchestra,

276
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:42,920
so you found a way to help me enroll.

